scale = Vector2(0.93228966, 0.93228966)
theme_override_fonts/font = ExtResource("17_yaehf")
theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 16
text = "Everything I'd love you to work on while I'm sleeping

Please be careful not to break anything — and if something does go wrong, no worries, just leave a quick note explaining what happened so I can catch up in the morning.
Could you make it so that when I spill tomato sauce on the flattened pizza dough, the sprite changes to a pizza with sauce on it?
Feel free to add more ingredients too — you can follow the same approach I used for the tomato sauce, or do it however you think works best.

talk with des on adding some new sprites instead of these pictures

That's all I need for now. If you finish everything and want to keep going, go for it — thanks so much!"
horizontal_alignment = 1
autowrap_mode = 2

